{"tid":1048701,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高圖爾斯：皇馬訓練水平高過車路士好多","createTime":"2019-03-05T21:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T00:25:39.000Z","uid":57035,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6895cf16c6f932b249250dda27274d61eab0029b","tid":1048701,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T21:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>場場畀人當靶咁射 梗係train得好啦</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/9c/3f/thibaut-courtois-real-madrid-unveiling_1on1ij5vafjlm1vrpyh7wzryg0.jpg?t=514531685\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F9c%2F3f%2Fthibaut-courtois-real-madrid-unveiling_1on1ij5vafjlm1vrpyh7wzryg0.jpg%3Ft%3D514531685&h=fed5fe02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年夏天，高圖爾斯以3500萬歐元的轉會費，從車路士加盟了皇馬。轉投新東家後，高圖爾斯「敢說」的特質再一次閃現，他竟在採訪中直言，皇馬的訓練水平比車路士高多了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  高圖爾斯表示：「在訓練當中，你能看出皇馬的水平很高。我現在每天都在見證一件事拉莫斯是世界上最好的中堅。皇馬的水平明顯高於車路士。」在高圖爾斯看來，車路士的訓練水平比不過皇馬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  此前四個賽季，高圖爾斯一直在車路士效力，他是藍軍的主力門將。不過他的心卻一直在西班牙，車路士時期，高圖爾斯多次公開表示，他很懷念西班牙的時光，想要重新回到西班牙踢球。到了今夏，高圖爾斯如願以償，不過讓車路士尷尬的是，由於高圖爾斯的合約到明夏就到期，他們沒能從高圖爾斯身上賣出價格，只收穫到了3500萬歐元轉會費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  加盟皇馬後，高圖爾斯在皇馬的處境也不樂觀，盧比迪古手下的主力門將暫時還是拿華斯，高圖爾斯截至目前只出場過一次。"},{"pid":"8e9cfa47dee1748810358fa13387721e0f7c7319","tid":1048701,"uid":61724,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T21:39:25.000Z","msg":"無得怪佢 d後衛下下比人起到腳 完全唔撚識mak人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be042341ed83e0fb1d06c03b9486307806f2018","tid":1048701,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T21:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90b9f03cd7e23a2aa83c5378e1feb72329a750c","tid":1048701,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T21:55:06.000Z","msg":"歐聯 &gt; 歐霸"},{"pid":"6ab4465a4394c7a7ae6294ae0102246200022aeb","tid":1048701,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T21:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5834d79c7731087a3afdd3b3536f975e8c42cc01","tid":1048701,"uid":148203,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T22:01:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">25圖死翻入你老母個臭閪</span></span>"},{"pid":"c95fa990a4ecf0cc1957119a150429c30303de5d","tid":1048701,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T22:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f51b46054a7751643bef9732eea90c61b22584a","tid":1048701,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T22:02:21.000Z","msg":"25<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23065bfa4e3271a339459171269568838fe28f1f","tid":1048701,"uid":27675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T22:03:18.000Z","msg":"場場輸幾粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b75bdcf12ff60dcb7fa8ac35c27d33d2b968319","tid":1048701,"uid":57035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T22:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/063503_0f54aa8292d20fa1652b4508b83fc8ba.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-