Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/070249_d85662dfbdf866ad4e08cdd1d8780c73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F070249_d85662dfbdf866ad4e08cdd1d8780c73.png&h=26feb754&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5138d8bdd13367c92969a07d3519db4089e0038","tid":1048701,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:32:04.000Z","msg":"皇馬門將泰拔高圖爾斯認為，前線隊友應爭取更多入球：「要勝出比賽，就必須取得入球，己隊兩戰巴塞隆拿都辦不到，問題在於最後的傳送欠準。」<br />\n<br />\n最衰都係前面入得一粒<br />\n入多三粒咪晉級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71abbd4027e38cc2e7cc39592f1819a3ca54a293","tid":1048701,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:33:22.000Z","msg":"弱隊出鋼門，你哋識條鐵咩"},{"pid":"88fff04a5e98f9d683a757eae5fdd20bbf4bd6bc","tid":1048701,"uid":84613,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:03:12.000Z","msg":"盡快將 高圖爾斯 高圖爾斯 高圖爾斯 拋棄吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece8c1dcba074d02046fe730795e138133576a83","tid":1048701,"uid":11695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea3a382d8ce38818c59b8f03a0da64b42c7f9eca","tid":1048701,"uid":189109,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T22:43:20.000Z","msg":"訓練得咁好一定大勝AJAX啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:21:49.000Z","msg":"失球大勝"},{"pid":"55a2f9ff5a240fe4257d3222b931638b29a7bbba","tid":1048701,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:23:10.000Z","msg":"弱旅出鋼門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96ad08a748f09f008bbea07b5131c9cb0de35c6","tid":1048701,"uid":25345,"lik